#EXAMPLES#
.IP \[bu] 2
Create a SecureSdb object.
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var securesdb = new SecureSdb( \[dq]192.168.20.71\[dq], 11790 )
\f[R]
.fi
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
Create a SecureSdb object with a username and password.
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var securesdb = new SecureSdb(\[dq]sdbserver1\[dq],11810,\[dq]sdbadmin\[dq],\[dq]123\[dq])
\f[R]
.fi
